An example simulated data set for the Western stock

Cobs
A matrix of [sim x nyear]
Iobs
A 3D array of observed relative abundance indices dimensions [sim x index x year]
K
A vector nsim long of von Bertalanffy growth parameter K estimates
Linf
A vector nsim long of growth parameter Linf estimates (maximum length)
t0
A vector nsim long of growth parameter t0 estimates
M
A matrix of natural mortality rate at age [sim x age]
Bt
A vector nsim long of current biomass estimates
MSY
A vector nsim long of MSY estimates
BMSY
A vector nsim long of BMSY estimates
UMSY
A vector nsim long of UMSY estimates
a
A vector nsim long of Length-weight conversion parameter a W=aL^b
b
A vector nsim long of Length-weight conversion parameter b W=aL^b
nages
An integer value specifying the total number of age classes
ageM
A vector nsim long of estimates of age at 50 per cent maturity
M
A matrix of maturity at age [sim x age]
Bt_PI
A vector nsim long of current biomass estimates known perfectly (PI: Perfect Information)
UMSY_PI
A vector nsim long of UMSY nown perfectly (PI: Perfect Information)
CAA
A 3D array of catch at age observations [sim x age x year]
CAL
A vector of lengths representing the start-end points of the length bins corresponding to CAL data]
MPrec
A vector nsim long of the previous recommendations of the management procedure
